{"id":"guide/routing-overview","title":"Angular Routing","contents":"\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/aio/content/guide/routing-overview.md?message=docs%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"angular-routing\" translation-result=\"on\">Angular 路由<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#angular-routing\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\">Angular Routing<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#angular-routing\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在單頁應用中，你可以透過顯示或隱藏與特定元件相對應的部分來更改使用者看到的內容，而不用去伺服器獲取新頁面。使用者執行應用程式任務時，他們需要在定義好的不同<a href=\"guide/glossary#view\" title=\"檢視的定義\">檢視</a>之間移動。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">In a single-page app, you change what the user sees by showing or hiding portions of the display that correspond to particular components, rather than going out to the server to get a new page.\nAs users perform application tasks, they need to move between the different <a href=\"guide/glossary#view\" title=\"Definition of view\">views</a> that you have defined.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要處理從一個<a href=\"guide/glossary#view\">檢視</a>到下一個檢視的導航，請使用 Angular <strong><code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code></strong>。<strong><code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code></strong> 會透過將瀏覽器 URL 解釋為更改檢視的操作指令來啟用導航。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To handle the navigation from one <a href=\"guide/glossary#view\">view</a> to the next, you use the Angular <strong><code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code></strong>.\nThe <strong><code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code></strong> enables navigation by interpreting a browser URL as an instruction to change the view.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要瀏覽具有主要路由器功能的範例應用，請參閱<live-example name=\"router\"></live-example>。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To explore a sample app featuring the router's primary features, see the <live-example name=\"router\"></live-example>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" translation-result=\"on\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Prerequisites<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在建立路由之前，你應該熟悉以下內容：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Before creating a route, you should be familiar with the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">元件基礎</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">Basics of components</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">範本基礎</a></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">Basics of templates</a></p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">一個 Angular 應用程式 - 你可以使用 <a href=\"cli\">Angular CLI</a> 產生基本的 Angular 應用程式。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">An Angular app —you can generate a basic Angular application using the <a href=\"cli\">Angular CLI</a>.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-angular-routing\" translation-result=\"on\">瞭解 Angular 路由<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#learn-about-angular-routing\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2><h2 translation-origin=\"off\">Learn about Angular routing<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#learn-about-angular-routing\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"guide/router\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Common routing tasks\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">通用路由任務</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Common routing tasks</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">瞭解如何實現與 Angular 路由相關的許多常見任務。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn how to implement many of the common tasks associated with Angular routing.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">通用路由任務</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Common routing tasks</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/router-tutorial\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Routing SPA tutorial\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">單頁應用程式 (SPA) 路由課程</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Single-page applications (SPAs) routing tutorial</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一個涵蓋與 Angular 路由相關的模式的課程。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A tutorial that covers patterns associated with Angular routing.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">路由 SPA 課程</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Routing SPA tutorial</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/router-tutorial-toh\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Routing Tour of Heroes\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">英雄之旅擴充路由課程</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Tour of Heroes expanded routing tutorial</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">為 Tour of Heroes 課程新增更多路由特性。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Add more routing features to the Tour of Heroes tutorial.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">英雄路由之旅</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Routing Tour of Heroes</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/routing-with-urlmatcher\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Creating custom route matches tutorial\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">建立自訂路由匹配課程</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Creating custom route matches tutorial</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">一個課程，介紹如何將自訂匹配策略模式與 Angular 路由一起使用。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A tutorial that covers how to use custom matching strategy patterns with Angular routing.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">自訂路由匹配課程</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Custom route matches tutorial</p>\n    \n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/router-reference\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Router reference\">\n    <section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-result=\"on\">路由器參考</section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" translation-origin=\"off\">Router reference</section>\n    \n    <p translation-result=\"on\">描述一些核心路由器 API 概念。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Describes some core router API concepts.</p>\n    \n    <p class=\"card-footer\" translation-result=\"on\">路由器參考</p><p class=\"card-footer\" translation-origin=\"off\">Router reference</p>\n    \n  </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：2/28/2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - features\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n - scaling\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-10\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-11\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/router/Router\n - cli\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/glossary#view\n - guide/router\n - guide/router-reference\n - guide/router-tutorial\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n - guide/routing-overview#angular-routing\n - guide/routing-overview#angular-路由\n - guide/routing-overview#learn-about-angular-routing\n - guide/routi